# WFMC Project

Flutter app (Android / iOS / Web) for viewing Wimmera flood maps from QGIS Server.

## Startup Defaults

- **All studies enabled** on first launch
- **Only the 1% (1 in 100yr) layer per study** enabled â€” no other return periods
- One default base layer enabled: `Flood Investigation Study Areas`
- Defaults are computed at runtime from the WMS GetCapabilities response â€” not hardcoded
- Do NOT auto-change the layer selection on startup (no auto-locate)
- The map zooms to fit the WCMA boundary on startup

## Server Convention (source of truth)

- The app derives studies, layer names, and default visibility directly from the server's WMS Capabilities
- A "study" = any direct child of the root layer whose `Name` ends with ` Flood Depths`
- The "100yr" default layer = any child of a study whose `Name` contains `1% (1 in 100`
- Base layers = children of the `Base Layers` group (excluding `Wimmera CMA Boundary`, which is rendered locally from `assets/wcma_boundary.geojson`)
- A base layer is on by default if its `<Keyword>visible=true</Keyword>` is present
- Constants describing this convention live in `lib/config/app_config.dart`

## Locate Me Behaviour

- Triggered **only** by the user pressing the Locate Me FAB â€” never automatic
- Zooms to the user's GPS position
- Auto-selects the closest study's 100yr layers (replaces current selection)

## Study Reports

- `lib/config/study_metadata.dart` (`StudyReports`) is just a `Map<String, String>` of literal server study Name â†’ report PDF URL
- Used only for the "For more info see Final Report" link in the identify panel
- `displayNameFor()` strips the trailing ` Flood Depths` for UI labels

## Writing Constraints

- Only write files inside the `wfmc` project folder
- Do NOT modify the `pozi_base` QGIS project without explicit permission

## Key Files

| Path | Description |
|---|---|
| `lib/main.dart` | Entry point, tile cache init |
| `lib/config/app_config.dart` | Server convention constants, basemap config, org info |
| `lib/config/study_metadata.dart` | `StudyReports`: study Name â†’ report URL + display-name helper |
| `lib/screens/home_screen.dart` | Main map UI, all features |
| `lib/screens/about_screen.dart` | About Wimmera CMA page |
| `lib/services/settings_store.dart` | WMS endpoint + map-path defaults |
| `lib/services/wms_capabilities_service.dart` | Capabilities fetch + parse + cache |
| `lib/services/wms_tile_provider.dart` | WMS tile provider + offline cache |
| `lib/services/wms_feature_info_service.dart` | GetFeatureInfo client |
| `lib/services/location_service.dart` | GPS wrapper |
| `lib/services/geocoding_service.dart` | Nominatim address search |
| `lib/services/bookmark_service.dart` | Saved locations CRUD |
| `lib/widgets/study_list.dart` | Studies + base layers selection UI |
| `lib/widgets/place_search_delegate.dart` | Address search UI |

## WMS Server

- Endpoint: `https://pozi.wcma.work/ows/`
- Map path: `/var/www/qgis_projects/pozi_base/pozi_base.qgs`
- Service title (root layer Name): `WCMA`
- CRS: EPSG:3857
- Format: image/png, transparent

## Running

```bash
flutter run -d edge     # Web (Edge)
flutter run -d chrome   # Web (Chrome)
flutter run             # Android device/emulator
```
